  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For two acute angles,&nbsp;<math alttext=\"angle upper Q\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>Q</mi></math> and <math alttext=\"angle upper R\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>R</mi></math>, <math alttext=\"cosine left parenthesis upper Q right parenthesis equals sine left parenthesis upper R right parenthesis\"><mi>cos</mi><mfenced><mi>Q</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mi>sin</mi><mfenced><mi>R</mi></mfenced></math>. The measures, in degrees, of&nbsp;<math alttext=\"angle upper Q\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>Q</mi></math> and&nbsp;<math alttext=\"angle upper R\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>R</mi></math> are <math alttext=\"x plus 61\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t<mn>61</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math> and <math alttext=\"4 x plus 4\"><mrow>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mn>4</mn>\n\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t</mrow>\n\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t<mn>4</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math>, respectively. What is the value of <math alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
